{"title":"使用Mybatis时，在插入一条数据记录返回主键id值","date":"2018-08-19T01:12:00.000Z","link":"post/206","categories":["Mybatis"],"updated":"2019-04-27T13:03:29.041Z","content":"<p>使用MyBatis往数据库中插入一条记录后，返回该条记录的主键值。</p>\n<p><code>useGeneratedKeys=true</code>默认为 false。当设置为 true 时，表示如果插入的表以自增列为主键，则允许 JDBC 支持自动生成主键，并可将自动生成的主键返回。<br><strong>两者最好一起用</strong></p>\n<p><code>useGeneratedKeys=true keyProperty=&quot;company_id&quot;</code><br>这个意思就是说。 他在插入后， 会自动把插入的数据生成的ID<br>塞入到你这个 keyProperty 后面设置的 ID 这个参数里面。<br>执行之后 你直接取ID 的值就好了。<br><figure class=\"highlight xml\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">insert</span> <span class=\"attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"save\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">useGeneratedKeys</span>=<span class=\"string\">true</span>  <span class=\"attr\">parameterType</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"pd\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">keyProperty</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"company_id\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tinsert into trtc_user_company_info(</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t···</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tid</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t) values (</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t···</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tnull <span class=\"comment\">&lt;!-- 填null时数据库默认自增 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">insert</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>获取已插入数据库中信息的id<br><figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pd.put(<span class=\"string\">\"COMPANY_ID\"</span>, pd.get(<span class=\"string\">\"company_id\"</span>));</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n","prev":{"title":"Linux查找某个目录下包含某个字段的文件","link":"post/215"},"next":{"title":"order by 多字段排序","link":"post/192"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/206/"}